@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Product Roadmap";
}

<h1 class="display-4 mb-4">🛣️ Product Roadmap</h1>
<p class="lead">Here's a preview of features planned for upcoming releases. These focus on improving match quality, fairness, and scheduling intelligence.</p>

<hr class="my-4" />

<h3>🔍 1. View Quality Information for Suggested Game</h3>
<p>Give users insights into why a game was suggested, including criteria like player balance, match fairness, and diversity of opponents. This will increase transparency and user trust.</p>

<h3>📊 2. Quality Reports for Sessions</h3>
<p>Enable viewing of a session-wide or historical quality report showing how well games met key quality indicators (e.g., rating balance, court usage, and player variety).</p>

<h3>⏳ 3. Lookahead Scheduling</h3>
<p>Predict when each game will end based on current scheduling, and use this to suggest matches that leave good options for future picks. This improves long-term court utilization.</p>

<h3>🎯 4. Better Handling for Extreme Ratings</h3>
<p>Ensure that players with very high or very low ratings get a good session experience, without being sidelined or matched poorly. This includes both fair pairing and equitable court time.</p>

<h3>⚖️ 5. Adjustable Game Scoring Weights</h3>
<p>Let users or clubs adjust weights in the game quality scoring algorithm. This allows prioritizing fairness, court usage, or diversity based on their specific needs.</p>

<hr class="my-5" />

<p class="text-muted"><em>Note: Features and priorities may evolve based on user feedback and technical constraints.</em></p>
